superccd2dng (1.4.0) stable; urgency=low

  * Add preview shadow recovery and shadow-range controls
  * Add selectable preview methods with Reconstruction and Amaze debayer modes
  * Improve preview rendering with reduced false color, better 6 MP Amaze output, and preserved zoom on file changes
  * Wrap the preview controls panel in a scroll area to keep the main layout usable at smaller heights

